metadata.name: Lua #15
metadata.description:
"I journey to the world of the moon,
Where life is less burdensome,
Where all gaze upon me, unaware
Of my presence in this lunar realm.

Yet darkness occasionally envelops me,
Leaves me lost and unsure.
But in the end, it is worth it all,
For on the moon, I am admired and loved,
Connected to others, despite being unseen."

~ Eduxdux + GPT

Made with p5.js, chroma.js and p5.grain

metadata.name: Flossom #138
metadata.description: This work is a research of flow fields, exploring generative art forms and colors. It uses various drawing methods, randomized color palettes, and layers of patterns to add multiple dimensions of variety to the work. Willing to create a visual blossom.
